Washing Burgundy Wigs
Use sulfate-free shampoo and conditioner to maintain human hair wigs color and texture. Wash burgundy colored wigs every 10-15 wears.https://yolowig.com/collections/human-hair-wigs

Styling Burgundy Wigs
Avoid excessive heat styling to prevent damage to human hair wigs. Use heat tools or heat protection spray to heat colored wigs if needed.https://yolowig.com/collections/colored-wigs

Storing Burgundy Wigs
Store human hair wigs on burgundy wigs stand to maintain the shape of colored wigs and prevent tangling.https://yolowig.com/collections/burgundy-wigs
